==English==

===Etymology===
From [[w:Osborne Reynolds|Osborne Reynolds]] British engineer

===Noun===
'''[[Reynolds]] [[number]]'''

#{{physics}} a [[dimensionless]] [[parameter]] that determines the behaviour of [[viscous]] [[flow]] [[patterns]]; a value less than about 2,000 producing [[laminar flow]], one above about 3,000 producing [[turbulent flow]] (intermediate values producing unpredictable behaviour)

